2) Type mismatches / incorrect return-type assumptions in processors:
- Several lines in processors assume entityService.updateItem (and similar) returns CompletableFuture<ObjectNode>, but the EntityService interface declares updateItem/addItem/etc. as returning CompletableFuture<UUID> (or different types). Compiler errors show:
