    - ReleaseReservationProcessor.java: similar.
    - ReserveInventoryProcessor.java: similar.

3) (Earlier errors were addressed) Some earlier errors about missing ProcessorSerializer methods and non-existent Totals constructor were fixed. The current blockers are the two categories above.

